# Project Intelligence Report: PoliceIT Analytics Core (PAC)

PoliceIT Analytics Core (PAC) is a custom investigation intelligence platform designed for the Karnataka State Police (KSP). PAC acts as an intelligence layer above existing systems (like CCTNS) to convert static crime records into actionable investigative intelligence using semantic search, geospatial analytics, and criminal network graphs.

---

